Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.72,0:24:39.72,On Screen red,,0,0,0,,[...a mysterious man appeared, wielding an incredible power!!]
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.72,0:24:45.02,On Screen red,,0,0,0,,[See you next time!]
